cff-version: 1.2.0
message: "If you use marinaMoji Kaeriten office plugins, please cite them as below."
type: software
title: marinaMoji Kaeriten
abstract: >-
  Office-suite extensions that render marinaMoji Unicode kaeriten marks into
  scholarly layout in LibreOffice, Microsoft Word, and ONLYOFFICE. Companion
  to the marinaMoji IME; canonical text remains ordinary Unicode (e.g. 說㆒㆑者).
authors:
